        desc: "Support for those who need to renew an existing visa and wish to prepare their documentation in an organized manner."
      },
      {
        title: "Student Visa",
        desc: "Guidance for people interested in studying in the United States and understanding the general steps of the process."
      },
      {
        title: "Work Visa",
        desc: "General information and guidance for individuals who want to understand options related to work visas."
      },
      {
        title: "Family Visa",
        desc: "Guidance for processes related to family members, reunification, and document preparation."
      },
      {
        title: "Work Permits",
        desc: "Help in understanding general requirements, preparing forms, and organizing documents related to work permits."
      },
      {
        title: "Adjustment of Status",
        desc: "General guidance for individuals wishing to better understand the process of adjustment of status within the United States."
      },
      {
        title: "Form Preparation",
        desc: "Assistance in preparing, reviewing, and organizing immigration forms, based on the information provided by the client."
      },
      {
        title: "Immigration Orientation",
        desc: "Personalized consultation to review the case, explain general options, and guide the client on the next steps."
      }
    ],
    requestBtn: "Request details",

    // Why Us
    whyTitle: "Why receive orientation with us?",
    benefits: [
      "We explain the process in clear and simple language",
      "We help organize important documents",
      "We provide personalized attention",
      "We guide the Latino community in Spanish",
      "We review the information carefully",
      "We accompany you step-by-step professionally",
      "We prevent confusion and disorganization during the process",
      "We offer a human, responsible, and reliable service"
    ],

    // Process
    processTitle: "How the process works",
    steps: [
      {
        num: "Step 1",
        title: "Initial consultation",
        desc: "We listen to your situation and understand what type of guidance you need."
      },
      {
        num: "Step 2",
        title: "Information review",
        desc: "We review the information and documents you have available."
      },
      {
        num: "Step 3",
        title: "Process organization",
        desc: "We help you identify which documents may be necessary and how to sort them."
      },
      {
        num: "Step 4",
        title: "Form preparation",
        desc: "We guide you in preparing forms and key information."
      },
      {
        num: "Step 5",
        title: "Support and follow-up",
        desc: "We guide you during the process so you have greater clarity at each stage."
      }
    ],

    // Required Documents
    docsTitle: "Documents you might need",
    docsText: "Documents may vary based on the type of visa, personal situation, and applicable requirements. Therefore, we recommend a personalized consultation before starting the process.",
    docItems: [
      "Valid passport",
      "Personal identification",
      "Passport-style photographs, if applicable",
      "Family information",
      "Employment or academic information",
      "Travel history",
      "Financial documents",
      "Letters or support related to the reason for travel",
      "Previous immigration documents, if applicable"
    ],

    // Gallery
    galleryTitle: "Preparation & Information Gallery",
    gallery: [
      {
        img: "/assets/images/project_visa_documents.png",
        alt: "Preparation of immigration documents in Newark New Jersey"
      },
      {
        img: "/assets/images/project_visa_consultation.png",
        alt: "Orientation for US visa applications"
      },
      {
        img: "/assets/images/project_visa_passport.png",
        alt: "Tourist visa advice for the United States"
      }
    ],

    // FAQ
    faqTitle: "Frequently Asked Questions about Visas",
    faqs: [
      {
        q: "Do you guarantee visa approval?",
        a: "No. No service can guarantee visa approval. Our job is to guide you, help you organize your information, and prepare you clearly and professionally."
      },
      {
        q: "Can you help me with a visa renewal?",
        a: "Yes. We can guide you in organizing documents and general preparation for the renewal process."
      },
      {
        q: "Can I receive guidance if I don't know which visa I need?",
        a: "Yes. We can review your general situation and explain common options so you better understand which path might apply to your case."
      },
      {
        q: "Do you help with immigration forms?",
        a: "Yes. We can help you with form preparation, review, and organization based on the information you provide."
      },
      {
        q: "Do you serve in Spanish?",
        a: "Yes. We offer orientation in Spanish for the Latino community."
      },
      {
        q: "Where are you located?",
        a: "Our main office is focused in Newark, New Jersey, and we can also guide clients from other areas depending on availability."
      },
      {
        q: "Can I consult via WhatsApp?",
        a: "Yes. You can contact us via WhatsApp to request more details or schedule a consultation."
      }
    ],

    // Final CTA
    finalCtaTitle: "Don't start your process with doubts",
    finalCtaText: "Receive clear orientation, organize your documents, and move forward with greater confidence alongside committed professionals.",
    whatsappCta: "Speak via WhatsApp"
  },
  pt: {
    heroTitle: "Solicitações de Visto para os Estados Unidos",
    heroSubtitle: "Ajudamos você a entender suas opções, organizar seus documentos e se preparar com clareza para o seu processo de visto americano.",
    requestOrient: "Solicitar orientação",
    whatsappLink: "Falar por WhatsApp",
    scheduleConsult: "Agendar consulta",
    badgeAccent: "Orientação USCIS e Consular",
    
    // Intro
    introTitle: "Orientação Clara e Profissional",
    introText: "Sabemos que iniciar uma solicitação de visto pode gerar muitas dúvidas: qual formulário preencher, quais documentos separar, como estruturar os dados e que etapas seguir. Por isso, oferecemos orientação profissional para ajudá-lo a compreender melhor o fluxo do processo e preparar-se de forma organizada. Nosso foco é acompanhá-lo com informações claras, atenção personalizada e um guia simples para que você possa avançar com mais segurança.",
